=head1 DESCRIPTION

Searches for a particular search term.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 MatchType => Str

Specifies how Deadline Cloud matches your search term in the results.
If you don't specify a C<matchType> the default is C<FUZZY_MATCH>.

=over

=item *

C<FUZZY_MATCH> - Matches if a portion of the search term is found in
the result.

=item *

C<CONTAINS> - Matches if the exact search term is contained in the
result.

=back



=head2 B<REQUIRED> SearchTerm => Str

The term to search for.



